Third-Party and Demo Asset Notices
----------------------------------

Bundled demo assets are included for starter and demo use, and remain subject
to their upstream terms. Replace the sample assets before publishing a
production site if your project needs a different licensing workflow.

Fonts:

- `src/assets/fonts/pretendard-variable.woff2`:
  A subset of Pretendard by Kil Hyung-jin, licensed under the SIL Open Font
  License 1.1.
  https://github.com/orioncactus/pretendard

- `src/assets/fonts/source-code-pro-latin-400-normal.woff2`:
  A Latin subset of Source Code Pro by Adobe, licensed under the SIL Open Font
  License 1.1.
  https://github.com/adobe-fonts/source-code-pro

Sample images:

- `src/assets/tone-sample-glass-building.jpg`:
  Pexels, Konstantin Olsen,
  "Contemporary glass building facade with reflections in the city."
  https://www.pexels.com/photo/blue-glass-building-287263/
- `src/assets/tone-sample-glass-grid.jpg`:
  Pexels, Michael Li, "Glass Modern Architecture."
  https://www.pexels.com/photo/glass-modern-architecture-17159619/
- `src/assets/tone-sample-blue-architecture.jpg`:
  Unsplash, Mikita Yo, "blue and white glass walled high rise building."
  https://unsplash.com/photos/blue-and-white-glass-walled-high-rise-building-wN6w_UHsARY
- `src/assets/tone-sample-ai-water.jpg`:
  AI-generated sample image created for Tone demo content; not sourced from a
  stock-photo provider.

References:

- Pexels License: https://www.pexels.com/license/
- Unsplash License: https://unsplash.com/license
- Unsplash attribution guidance: https://help.unsplash.com/en/articles/2511315-guideline-attribution
- Unsplash usage guidance: https://help.unsplash.com/en/articles/2612337-do-i-have-to-give-credit-to-a-contributor-when-i-use-their-image

Favicon and app icons:

`public/favicon.svg`, `public/favicon.ico`, `public/favicon-16x16.png`,
`public/favicon-32x32.png`, and `public/apple-touch-icon.png` are Tone project
marks and are covered by this repository's license.

